<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark sticky-top">
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="<%= site_home_index_path %>">
        <%= image_tag 'logo.png', alt: 'RubyTrivia Logo', style: 'height: 45px;' %>
        <span class="ms-2">Ruby Trivia</span>
      </a>

      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
        <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
          <!-- Links da navbar esquerda -->
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Login Button -->
  <div class="login-button">
    <%= link_to users_backoffice_home_index_path, class: "btn btn-outline-danger" do %>
      <%= t('Login') %>
    <% end %>
  </div><br>

  <main role="main">
    <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes -->
    <div class="container marketing">
      <!-- Centered image with overlay text -->
      <div class="container" style="height: 50vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center; position: relative; margin-bottom: 50px; padding-top: 100px; z-index: 1;">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12" style="position: relative;">
            <%= image_tag '03.png', alt: 'Centered Image', style: 'max-width: 100%; height: auto;' %>
            <div class="centered-content">
              <h2>Ruby Trivia</h2>
              <p>Discover Ruby Trivia, an application by DevThree designed to assist new programmers in mastering Ruby on Rails.</p>
              <% if user_signed_in? %>
                <p><%= link_to "Get Started »", users_backoffice_home_index_path, class: "btn btn-danger btn-sm", role: "button" %></p>
              <% else %>
                <p><%= link_to "Get Started »", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-danger btn-sm", role: "button" %></p>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><br><br><br>

      <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

      <div class="row featurette text-white">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Free Ruby on Rails Learning Platform: Master the Framework</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            Explore our free learning platform for mastering Ruby on Rails. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced developer, our comprehensive resources cover everything from fundamentals to advanced techniques. Dive into real-world projects, learn efficient development practices, and join a vibrant community of learners. Start coding today and unleash the power of Rails to advance your career in tech.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag '01.png', alt: 'Rails Image', class: 'featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto', width: '420', height: '420' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

      <div class="row featurette text-white">
        <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Ruby on Rails in Major Enterprises: Driving Efficiency and Innovation</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            Ruby on Rails (Rails) has become pivotal in enterprise software development for its simplicity, robustness, and agility. This framework accelerates time-to-market by emphasizing convention over configuration, making it ideal for scalable applications that evolve with enterprise growth. With a rich ecosystem of plugins and a developer-friendly codebase, Rails supports diverse enterprise needs from e-commerce to analytics, fostering collaboration and innovation. By adhering to DRY and MVC principles, Rails ensures code maintainability and scalability, crucial for large-scale deployments. As enterprises prioritize agility and innovation, Rails continues to empower efficient, scalable solutions that drive competitive advantage and exceptional user experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
          <%= image_tag '05.png', alt: '250x250', class: 'featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto', width: '420', height: '420' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">

      <div class="row featurette text-white">
        <div class="col-md-7">
          <h2 class="featurette-heading">Sign in and Start Using the Tool Now!</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            Unlock your access to our powerful tool by signing in today. Dive into a wealth of resources and features designed to enhance your experience from the moment you log in. Join a vibrant community of learners and developers, ready to support your journey in mastering Ruby on Rails and beyond.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5">
          <%= image_tag '02.png', alt: '500x500', class: 'featurette-image img-fluid mx-auto', width: '420', height: '420' %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="featurette-divider" style="height: 2px; border-width: 0; background-color: #000;">
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer class="mt-auto">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center">
            <a href="/" class="mb-3 me-2 mb-md-0 text">
              <%= image_tag 'logo_devthree.png', alt: 'Logo', width: '70', height: '70' %>
            </a>
            <span class="mb-3 mb-md-0 text-white">© 2024 DevThree, Inc</span>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-end">
            <ul class="nav">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=5548996046223&text=" target="_blank" class="nav-link px-2"><i class="bi bi-whatsapp fs-2"></i></a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/devthreebr/" target="_blank" class="nav-link px-2"><i class="bi bi-instagram fs-2"></i></a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a href="mailto:threetechnology2@gmail.com?subject=Assunto%20do%20E-mail" target="_blank" class="nav-link px-2"><i class="bi bi-envelope-at fs-2"></i></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
